OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWet on
OL,6,FSunday with rain breaking to showers,
OL,7,Fpossibly thundery. Showers easing
OL,8,Fduring Monday and Tuesday with sunnier
OL,9,Fspells emerging, but feeling less warm
OL,10,Fas temperatures drop closer to average.
